    "synopsis": {
        "native": "C\u00e2nd Radu afl\u0103 c\u0103 mai are doar c\u00e2teva luni de tr\u0103it, fuge p\u00e2n\u0103 ajunge \u00eentr-un sat izolat, la Nea Pavel, unde se refugiaz\u0103 \u00een c\u0103su\u021ba sa mic\u0103 din v\u00e2rful dealului. Timpul trece \u0219i Radu \u00eencepe s\u0103 tr\u0103iasc\u0103 o nou\u0103 via\u021b\u0103, uit\u00e2nd de a\u0219teptarea mor\u021bii \u0219i bucur\u00e2ndu-se de simplitatea clipei. El cutreier\u0103 \u00eemprejurimile \u00eempreun\u0103 cu b\u0103tr\u00e2nul, \"c\u0103ut\u00e2nd v\u00e2nt\". Dar c\u00e2nd \u00ee\u0219i d\u0103 seama c\u0103 s-a \u00eendr\u0103gostit de o femeie din sat, \u00ee\u0219i aminte\u0219te de sf\u00e2r\u0219itul s\u0103u iminent. Unde \u00eel va purta v\u00e2ntul mai departe?",
